author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Really I'm happy too...
Rushia-daitenshi is very cute with New Year Outfit. :_ちょうちょ:

As curiosity: that Live2D was the first modeling made by Tou Irie, who later remodeled Fumi's first form a few weeks or few months later (Private Video) and later modeled her New Live2D for premiering at 2020 June 16th.
Tou Irie's modelings on Rushia went more closer to Kamiki Kinu in appearance (Kamiki Kinu was the first Yasuyuki-sensei's vtuber creation and PLIVyou's founder member, but sadly graduated at 2019 May 31st) 

I was watching the live, but also starting to feel the effects of New Year... Even the drinking was... Oh, also drinking and planning for 2021.
Let's go for this successful 2021.

Postscript: hugs for all fandeads... :_きゅん:

0:00 Opening Graphics / Japanese New Year Music - Probably Free-use BGM

7:32 Rushia's planning for this year
Categories: Goals / EveryDay / Human Relations / 3D / Idol

Post delivery chat and SuperChat reading Time ("Thank you Time" logo)

1:03:21 Rushia tries to search BGM...
1:04:09 Powerful BGM. Cute headbanging.

Ending Words: "I hope that you can spend all this year smiling with everyone. Otsurushi~" ☺

Happy 2021 for all Viewers, Fandeads, Members, and of course Rushia.
